responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "0C518C4E46CF448BA5F30288CA07A768", "And storm into Nika\'brae on my own? These days they\'ve taken up garrisons reinforced by many legions of armed cutthroats on duty. They may have once been a motley crew, but ever since they\'ve spread their numbers West of the gates, they\'re covering ground faster than we can. Don\'t get me wrong, they\'re no more threatening than a pack of angry wolves, but personally? I wouldn\'t go knocking at their front gates without a direct order from above.")
